      "content": "it's just hard to believe anyone actually cares. even if they do, they aren't him. i look at his side of the bed every morning and it feels like a physical weight on my chest. it feels like i'm just holding onto a life that was meant to be shared, and now it's just a burden to carry alone. it feels so much more logical to just let go of it all.",
